
Official Kubernetes Ingress Controllers
NGINX Ingress Controller – Most widely used, supports annotations & ConfigMaps for customization.
Kong Ingress Controller – API gateway with authentication, rate-limiting, and transformations.
Traefik Ingress Controller – Lightweight, supports automatic TLS via Let’s Encrypt.
HAProxy Ingress Controller – High-performance, reliable, with advanced TCP/HTTP routing.
Contour Ingress Controller – Backed by Envoy Proxy, designed for high scalability.
Cloud Provider-Specific Ingress Controllers
AWS ALB Ingress Controller – Uses AWS ALB for dynamic routing and load balancing.
GCE Ingress Controller – Google Cloud’s native ingress solution.
Azure Application Gateway Ingress Controller – Integrates with Azure’s L7 load balancer.
Service Mesh-Based Ingress Controllers
Istio Ingress Gateway – Works with Istio for traffic management & security.
Linkerd Ingress Controller – Integrated with Linkerd for mTLS & observability.
Consul Ingress Controller – From HashiCorp, for secure service-to-service communication.
